{"tid":423282,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"假如每個領域嘅精英分別統治唔同國家","createTime":"2017-10-03T18:32:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-04T04:47:18.000Z","uid":43414,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"8f8b49ec3b630c363197bb5be071cc9353db83d5","tid":423282,"uid":43414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T18:32:19.000Z","msg":"例如經濟學嘅精英統治一個國家，負責經濟運作<br />\n能源學嘅精英又統治一個國家，負責能源生產嗰啲<br />\n而裹面嘅人冇分種族咁去居住，<br />\n剩係跟翻嗰個人嘅特長分翻去相應嘅國家<br />\n咁樣嘅話呢個世界會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6870e2b3367824a6b0d9d8cab95b009ff3d8ebae","tid":423282,"uid":62915,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T18:51:09.000Z","msg":"你都ff到一個咁奇特嘅設定出黎，<br />\n點解唔ff埋個結果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b922a6f7824e36606ade1b7e680c1e31e7fa3418","tid":423282,"uid":43414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T19:05:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你都ff到一個咁奇特嘅設定出黎，<br />\n點解唔ff埋個結果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 集思廣益"},{"pid":"dff2a2456766b1d83c22230d311566ab304feaee","tid":423282,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T19:08:13.000Z","msg":"ff專家會贏"},{"pid":"aaff477e5e71659d4222f18eee929b31cad2ee0c","tid":423282,"uid":103497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T19:15:52.000Z","msg":"掌握生產力既國家會玩曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70077555f8a2f9517f100c17093289747bbbc8e2","tid":423282,"uid":37241,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T19:25:46.000Z","msg":"唔係好明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n即係洗碗又一個國家<br />\n運輸又一個國家??<br />\n咁個國家點運作？"},{"pid":"b4979783a16af8866b7de386b9761d3b9918c633","tid":423282,"uid":43414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T19:31:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔係好明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n即係洗碗又一個國家<br />\n運輸又一個國家??<br />\n咁個國家點運作？</blockquote><br />\n係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以要同其他國家合作<br />\n用等價交換嚟換其他嘢去長期支撐國家運作"},{"pid":"a7bb0ea6da4346ce680994cfe603837f3a2050d1","tid":423282,"uid":54927,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T19:33:07.000Z","msg":"onlun9"},{"pid":"f6f8ad94b677d4095e7cb89b76e8f624ef934a18","tid":423282,"uid":43414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T19:34:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>掌握生產力既國家會玩曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢個世界冇公平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點樣令一啲「冇咁重要」嘅領域不被貶值侵佔係一個問題"},{"pid":"6d24876370f53f7edc4e6f6efe217cf95783c607","tid":423282,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T19:35:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>onlun9</blockquote><br />\n唔係呀 幾有趣"},{"pid":"2dd2c921642c6366db0188f765669dac7a2a1d95","tid":423282,"uid":127727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T19:36:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>例如經濟學嘅精英統治一個國家，負責經濟運作<br />\n能源學嘅精英又統治一個國家，負責能源生產嗰啲<br />\n而裹面嘅人冇分種族咁去居住，<br />\n剩係跟翻嗰個人嘅特長分翻去相應嘅國家<br />\n咁樣嘅話呢個世界會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n會出現資源錯配，leader都錯配，統治國家既人最主要係識點分配人去合適既位置，其他都係其次。"},{"pid":"51c04c1cdb8462531ec250b5ba72b0a82aaf0413","tid":423282,"uid":123825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T19:47:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔係好明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n即係洗碗又一個國家<br />\n運輸又一個國家??<br />\n咁個國家點運作？</blockquote><br />\n如果係咁會有少少似共產主義嘅計劃經濟"},{"pid":"a754c37b164aee9228fbe244f5308340224e67f0","tid":423282,"uid":72424,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T19:47:53.000Z","msg":"會出現排斥<br />\n例如 <br />\nA國係負責工程 <br />\nB國係負責金融<br />\nC國係負責科技<br />\n<br />\nA國可以私底下同C國合作<br />\n排斥B國 <br />\nB國既經濟無咁好 啲精英就會外流去其他國家<br />\n久而久之結果就同現實生活無分別"},{"pid":"10d2882e58d77ad5a2112cb39d4eb2906226eb46","tid":423282,"uid":70375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T04:45:41.000Z","msg":"掌握軍事嘅會打哂全世界"},{"pid":"965a58cda4510f572a948db8698f8c9b1fb21496","tid":423282,"uid":36111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T04:47:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>ff專家會贏</blockquote><br />\n國屍"}]}